Package: imrchart
Title: Individuals and Moving Range Charts
Date: 2016-05-27
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Author: person("Maurice", "Klaus", email = "mbklaus@gmail.com", role = c("aut",
    "cre"))
Description: This packages creates an individuals and moving range chart from
    a single, numeric data vector. The charts are based on the inviduals and moving
    range charts described in 'Understanding Statistical Process Control' by Donald
    Wheeler and David Chambers. The charts accommodate the 8 Western Electric
    control chart tests.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1.9000
